msgctxt "0002"
msgid "Absolutely!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>As things progress during each class trial, you will\n"
"engage in a number of <CLT><CLT 3>Nonstop Debates<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>During these discussions, characters will speak one\n"
"after another, <CLT><CLT 3>without pause<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>It's up to you to unearth any <CLT><CLT 3>lies or contradictions<CLT><CLT 23>\n"
"buried within their statements.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>What this means is that you'll have to use your <CLT><CLT 3>Truth\n"
"Bullets<CLT><CLT 23> to <CLT><CLT 3>refute<CLT><CLT 23> what they say.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Any relevant <CLT><CLT 3>Truth Bullets<CLT><CLT 23> you've found during your\n"
"investigation will be loaded into the <CLT><CLT 3>Truth Cylinder<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Use the <CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_LEFT_STICK%<CLT><CLT 23> to aim, then fire with \n"
"the <CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_TRIAL_SHOOT%<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>â€¦\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Pay close attention to each character's <CLT><CLT 3>statements<CLT><CLT 23>,\n"
"and use your <CLT><CLT 3>Truth Bullets<CLT><CLT 23> to blast the right ones.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Note that if you run out of time, you will\n"
"automatically <CLT><CLT 3>fail<CLT><CLT 23>, so please be careful!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>If you press the <CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_SHOW_HELP%<CLT><CLT 23> during these\n"
"arguments, you can review the <CLT><CLT 3>controls<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Well then...good luck, and have fun!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Your first <CLT><CLT 3>Nonstop Debate<CLT><CLT 23> is about to begin. Would\n"
"you like to hear more?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
